'''尋找'''（{{lang-en|Find My}}）是[[蘋果公司|蘋果公司]]於2019年推出的应用和服务<ref>{{Cite web|title=Find My - Official Apple Support|url=https://support.apple.com/explore/find-my|accessdate=2019-10-09|work=support.apple.com|archive-date=2020-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201016091723/https://support.apple.com/explore/find-my|dead-url=no}}</ref>，用户可以通過該功能尋找、追踪和定位[[iOS|iOS]]、[[iPadOS|iPadOS]]、[[MacOS|MacOS]]、[[WatchOS|WatchOS]]、[[AirPods|AirPods]]、[[AirTag|AirTags]]等设备所處的位置{{Refnest|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.cnet.com/how-to/use-the-new-find-my-app-to-hunt-down-your-friends-and-your-iphone/|title=Use the new Find My app to hunt down your friends and your iPhone|website=[[CNET|CNET]]|access-date=2019-10-10|date=September 21, 2019|first=Jason|last=Cipriani|archive-date=2020-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201016092010/https://www.cnet.com/how-to/use-the-new-find-my-app-to-hunt-down-your-friends-and-your-iphone/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|first=Dan|last=Moren|access-date=2019-11-07|title=iOS 13 Find My App: How to Track Your iPhone or Friends|url=https://www.tomsguide.com/reference/how-to-track-your-iphone-or-friends|website=[[Tom's_硬體指南|Tom's 硬體指南]]|date=September 8, 2019|archive-date=2020-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201016092036/https://www.tomsguide.com/reference/how-to-track-your-iphone-or-friends|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|first1=Jonny|last1=Evans|access-date=2019-11-07|title=How 'Find My' Mac works in macOS Catalina and iOS 13|url=https://www.computerworld.com/article/3404498/how-find-my-mac-works-in-macos-catalina-and-ios-13.html|date=21 June 2019|website=[[Computerworld|Computerworld]]|archive-date=2020-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201016092100/https://www.computerworld.com/article/3404498/how-find-my-mac-works-in-macos-catalina-and-ios-13.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|access-date=2019-11-07|title=Apple's 'Find My' Feature Uses Some Very Clever Cryptography|url=https://www.wired.com/story/apple-find-my-cryptography-bluetooth/|newspaper=[[连线|连线]]|issn=1059-1028|first=Andy|last=Greenberg|author-link=Andy Greenberg|date=June 5, 2019|archive-date=2020-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201016092126/https://www.wired.com/story/apple-find-my-cryptography-bluetooth/|dead-url=no}}</ref>}}。

== 历史 ==
Find My 于2019年9月19日与iOS 13一起发布， 将以前的 Find My Friends 和Find My iPhone（在 macOS 设备上称为 Find My Mac）的功能合并到一个应用程序中。

2021年4月起，用戶可以通過該功能追蹤和定位非蘋果公司出品的第三方设备<ref>{{Cite web|title=苹果的 Find My 网络正式向第三方设备开放|url=https://cn.engadget.com/apple-find-my-third-party-010051420.html|author=engadget}}</ref>。

